description: Demolition of Elizabeth House Park Lane, 1-32 Mickleham Gardens, 1-12 Pond Hill Gardens, 23-27 Malden Road and 1-3 Cheam Parkway,Cheam and erection of four 2-storey buildings with roof accommodation to provide a total of 131 dwellings for the vulnerable and/or the elderly comprising ninety seven 1-bedroomed and nineteen 2-bedroomed self contained flats (affordable) and fifteen 2-bedroomed self contained flats (general sale) together with communal and ancillary accommodation, guest rooms, buggy and cycle stores, 43 car parking spaces, refuse and recycling facilities and vehicular accesses from Pond Hill Gardens and Mickleham Gardens.
